model.interpreter.core

Class FetchVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.interpreter.core.FetchVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IResumeVisitor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    HTMLVisitor, TimelineVisitor

    public abstract class FetchVisitor
extends java.lang.Object
implements IResumeVisitor
    This visitor reads a given model and stores all information in several members. To write an own interpreter this visitor can be overridden and therefore the functionality is to be implemented in the method IResumeVisitor.perform(String) .
    Author:
    Christoph Petzold
